{"tid":2309104,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(正視聽)黃之鋒、周庭同12港人一樣永遠不可能獲得釋放，除非成功戰勝支那共匪光復香港","createTime":"2020-12-02T10:19:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T16:05:53.000Z","uid":304769,"like":107,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"327171ce9a0939afc54251f33bb05cc9486c0386","tid":2309104,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T10:19:00.000Z","msg":"講真，佢哋根本唔係囚犯，佢哋係政治犯、戰俘。以<span class=\"red\">支那共匪對付政治犯</span>如李旺陽、劉曉波既歷史黎睇，最終<span class=\"red\">只會不停加控罪名延長刑期</span>，最後甚至喺<span class=\"red\">缺乏傳媒關注下被自殺</span>。千祈唔好低估支那共匪既冷血，長春圍城、六四屠城就係好例子。<br />\n<br />\n所以，我地<strong><span class=\"red\">為手足，即使不能街頭再聚，但係請大家唔好比放負L搞到放棄</span></strong>。即使喺網上以及世界各國，我地一樣可以出一分力。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">Twitter、各國支那領事館</span></strong>固然要人，但係大家仲有好多野可以做，例如推動制裁方面，其實各位<span class=\"red\"><strong>BNO抵步後可以立即登記選民以及參加政黨，並向你選區、黨既MP提出你對香港問題既睇法</strong></span>。其他國家公民(美、澳、紐、加)亦可以做類似既嘢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">為手足，縱使艱難，都要緊守崗位戰鬥到底。侵侵腹背受敵都未灰，各位手足灰乜春啊<br />\nWe shall never surrender </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e0312557bb2efd8aa1ea33738285ad0992906761","tid":2309104,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T10:19:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"90805f8f1b7bdc0a4e6729a58172b70e88d55e0c","tid":2309104,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T10:21:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"62d8d236ba857576afeb4ae58475b2de52746d15","tid":2309104,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T10:21:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf68874ed2a7529dc98122088703ff2f1258ca66","tid":2309104,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T10:21:38.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"978e50daa53952c0f58edc7f37fabc599c7