/strong>。即使喺網上以及世界各國，我地一樣可以出一分力。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">Twitter、各國支那領事館</span></strong>固然要人，但係大家仲有好多野可以做，例如推動制裁方面，其實各位<span class=\"red\"><strong>BNO抵步後可以立即登記選民以及參加政黨，並向你選區、黨既MP提出你對香港問題既睇法</strong></span>。其他國家公民(美、澳、紐、加)亦可以做類似既嘢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">為手足，縱使艱難，都要緊守崗位戰鬥到底。侵侵腹背受敵都未灰，各位手足灰乜春啊<br />\nWe shall never surrender </span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T15:26:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 堅持"},{"pid":"0c2e52cdd9a2c87546bcf435c37aef46030ee948","tid":2309104,"uid":10471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T15:28:07.000Z","msg":"這是一場革命<br />\n唯獨港人可取勝"},{"pid":"6317441feba7e82f2f2d5d7ce664bea3de2f1e1d","tid":2309104,"uid":188104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T15:29:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f5059f292106131c7ef5cb5d0f537fbf8e95c53","tid":2309104,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T15:30:11.000Z","msg":"唔該可唔可以幫我推兩推吖~<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> [請推上熱門] 應承我 可唔可以日日用呢一個hashtag推文? - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2309486\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2309486</a> #SendTroopsToLiberateHK"},{"pid":"aec64cf4e3f29ee563457570549d3752cefa1a64","tid":2309104,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f5059f29210